With Compose Music Video Editor you don t need to create the whole edit from scratch. You only need to select the transition template you like out of hundreds of advanced transition templates and add the media and music. The rest is done by Compose and you have an advanced edit! Share the edit on your social media and make your followers wonder how you got those editing skills. Features: Perfect beat timing for your music videos Hundred of advanced templates HD video export Photo slideshow maker 3 step video editing: Select the template you like Add photos videos to templates Add music to your video Stay tuned for the updates.
